ykathryn">Kelly Groves</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/kelseydamas">Kelsey Damas</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/kyleunzicker">Kyle Unzicker</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/mat-lipe">Mat Lipe</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/mattwiebe">Matt Wiebe</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/mdbitz">Matthew Denton</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/nickciske">Nick Ciske</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/mastromktg">Nick Mastromattei</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/paulhughes01">Paul Hughes</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/roblagatta">Rob La Gatta</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ryancurban">Ryan Urban</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/faction23">Samuel Estok</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/codearachnid">Timothy Wood</a></li>\n</ul>";s:7:"reviews";s:10651:"<p>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-avatar">\n		</div>\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n			<h4>Top Notch Plugin</h4>\n			<div class="star-rating"><span class="screen-reader-text">5.0 rating</span><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/oldhamtech"><img alt="" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/6a2e8c19de04bd629726061d33d4dac3?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g" class="photo avatar avatar-16" /></a>\n			<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/oldhamtech">oldhamtech</a> on\n			<span class="review-date">January 7, 2017</span>\n\n		</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">\n		Credit to the Team.\n\nIts a plug and play plugin innovation.\n\nPlease how can i change ticket sender which is currently showing WORDPRESS.\n\nI would like it to show the Programm Title instead of WORDPRESS.\n\nThanks as i await your response\n\nCheers to the Great Team	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-avatar">\n		</div>\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n			<h4>Nice rsvp plugin</h4>\n			<div class="star-rating"><span class="screen-reader-text">4.0 rating</span><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-empty"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/lukodp"><img alt="" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/79138dd90c1b4babb1b9dff8adee78d1?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g" class="photo avatar avatar-16" /></a>\n			<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/lukodp">lukodp</a> on\n			<span class="review-date">November 28, 2016</span>\n\n		</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">\n		This is very nice and useful plugin. \n4 stars is because I have to manually adjust stock when moving rsvp from one ticket to the other :)	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-avatar">\n		</div>\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n			<h4>Superior Plugin - Minimal Learning Curve</h4>\n			<div class="star-rating"><span class="screen-reader-text">5.0 rating</span><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/carestruckcurrent"><img alt="" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/e662682e448cd5c2ff54bcf991c0ed10?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g" class="photo avatar avatar-16" /></a>\n			<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/carestruckcurrent">Carestruckcurrent</a> on\n			<span class="review-date">November 26, 2016</span>\n\n		</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">\n		This plugin is intuitive, easy to use, and streamlined to give you your highest priority options right off the bat. Great experience!	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-avatar">\n		</div>\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n			<h4>Limited Functionality</h4>\n			<div class="star-rating"><span class="screen-reader-text">2.0 rating</span><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-empty"></div><div class="star star-empty"></div><div class="star star-empty"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/sallywolleat"><img alt="" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/735899a3ce16487aa02ad2f0c25aebec?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g" class="photo avatar avatar-16" /></a>\n			<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/sallywolleat">sally.wolleat</a> on\n			<span class="review-date">October 18, 2016</span>\n\n		</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">\n		If you would like to sell tickets for recurring events, look elsewhere. We purchased Events Calendar Pro and Events Tickets Plus with the [seemingly] simple goal of supporting two ticket types (Child and Adult) for events that were to occur 1-3 times per day for a few days in a row. Implementation has been a nightmare.\n\nIf you are not looking for recurring event support, this plugin/s might be fine for you.	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-avatar">\n		</div>\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n			<h4>Maximum tickets sold at a time</h4>\n			<div class="star-rating"><span class="screen-reader-text">4.0 rating</span><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-empty"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/zinizcheng77"><img alt="" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/14c32ef7b9c55732a8ae6f3f56fa5ac8?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g" class="photo avatar avatar-16" /></a>\n			<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/zinizcheng77">zinizcheng77</a> on\n			<span class="review-date">September 25, 2016</span>\n\n		</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">\n		Great ticket system within event calendar, so far so good for a free plugin.\n\nI will give one more star if you can limit the maximum tickets sold at a time. \n\nI have a free event with 2000 seats, one user responded to RSVP with 900 seats so that all tickets were out! Please add this function in this free plugin, and I am sure this is a great plugin	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-avatar">\n		</div>\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n			<h4>Auto reply customization</h4>\n			<div class="star-rating"><span class="screen-reader-text">1.0 rating</span><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-empty"></div><div class="star star-empty"></div><div class="star star-empty"></div><div class="star star-empty"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/pflyz"><img alt="" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/0b3e461c7dbf68fb0e95093c6bbb800d?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g" class="photo avatar avatar-16" /></a>\n			<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/pflyz">pflyz</a> on\n			<span class="review-date">September 3, 2016</span>\n\n		</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">\n		<p>This is not available- why would I pay $90 for something I can''t see work?\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-avatar">\n		</div>\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n			<h4>Excellent product</h4>\n			<div class="star-rating"><span class="screen-reader-text">5.0 rating</span><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/slb535"><img alt="" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/3566b1ec41306b87192961789938e9e1?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g" class="photo avatar avatar-16" /></a>\n			<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/slb535">slb535</a> on\n			<span class="review-date">September 3, 2016</span>\n\n		</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">\n		<p>This allowed us to transform our school''s annual variety show  from paper tickets to electronic, something we''d been trying to do for years.\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-avatar">\n		</div>\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n			<h4>Wonderful product</h4>\n			<div class="star-rating"><span class="screen-reader-text">5.0 rating</span><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tinydesignstudio"><img alt="" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/f9111a67b2abe1a050fe0aee31487aff?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g" class="photo avatar avatar-16" /></a>\n			<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/tinydesignstudio">tinydesignstudio</a> on\n			<span class="review-date">September 3, 2016</span>\n\n		</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">\n		<p>This tool has been beneficial in managing and promoting events for our nonprofit organization. I look forward to exploring all of the extended features.\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-avatar">\n		</div>\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n			<h4>Solid event ticketing</h4>\n			<div class="star-rating"><span class="screen-reader-text">5.0 rating</span><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/lukecavanagh"><img alt="" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/6d0f32a5e5bc24bb15ad104c81da7a70?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g" class="photo avatar avatar-16" /></a>\n			<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/lukecavanagh">Luke Cavanagh (lukecavanagh)</a> on\n			<span class="review-date">September 3, 2016</span>\n\n		</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">\n		<p>Really a well thought out product.\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-avatar">\n		</div>\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n			<h4>The best ticketing plugin for wordpress</h4>\n			<div class="star-rating"><span class="screen-reader-text">5.0 rating</span><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div><div class="star star-full"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/dzenzooma"><img alt="" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/38da4e007ee8a1f1a54b5374e1c5e2c8?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g" class="photo avatar avatar-16" /></a>\n			<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/dzenzooma">Jeff (dzenzooma)</a> on\n			<span class="review-date">September 3, 2016</span>\n\n		</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">\n		<p>I have been using products from the Tribe for a couple of years now and have been incredibly impressed by the team and the plugins. Thank you and keep up the excellent work.\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n";}s:13:"download_link";s:61:"http://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/event-tickets.4.4.4.zip";s:4:"tags";a:20:{s:3:"api